---
layout: base.njk
title: Initiatives
summary: "Eight strategic programs advancing data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology for the common good."
bodyClass: article
---
<article class="initiatives-page">
  <header class="essay-banner essay-banner-plain init-banner">
    <div class="essay-banner-inner">
      <p class="essay-kicker"><span class="essay-publication">Our Work</span></p>
      <h1 class="essay-title">Eight initiatives for the common good</h1>
      <p class="essay-dek">A comprehensive approach to ensuring data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology serve humanity, peace, and human dignity.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="ip-wrap">
    <p class="ip-intro">DCF advances its mission through eight interconnected initiatives, each addressing critical aspects of data sovereignty, sovereign AI, values-based AI programming, and emerging cyber technology. Together, they form a comprehensive approach to ensuring AI and emerging cyber technology serve the common good.</p>

    <nav class="ip-jump">
      {% for item in initiatives %}{% set slug = item.name | lower | replace("/", "-") | replace(" ", "-") %}<a href="#{{ slug }}">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }} {{ item.name }}</a>{% endfor %}
    </nav>

    {% for item in initiatives %}{% set slug = item.name | lower | replace("/", "-") | replace(" ", "-") %}
    <section class="ip-init" id="{{ slug }}">
      <div class="ip-num">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</div>
      <div class="ip-content">
        <h2 class="ip-name">{{ item.name }}</h2>
        {% if item.tagline %}<p class="ip-tagline">{{ item.tagline }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if item.description %}<p class="ip-desc">{{ item.description }}</p>{% endif %}
        {% if item.programs %}
        <ul class="ip-programs">
          {% for program in item.programs %}<li>{{ program }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </section>
    {% endfor %}

    <div class="ip-cta">
      <h2>Get involved</h2>
      <p>Partner with us, contribute your expertise, or support the work of advancing technology for the common good.</p>
      <a class="ip-btn" href="#">Get Involved</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
